h power optoelectronic and electronic devices that\nrequire both high crystalline quality and highly doped (Al,Ga)N films.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Feb 2016 19:20:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
